ith central symmetry are given by their corresponding\ndensest lattice packings. This is the analog of Kepler's sphere conjecture for\nthese solids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Aug 2009 23:05:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
