he relation between the interpolation expression and a diffusion\nmodel, which is derived in the paper, allows one to simulate the chaotic\nprocesses in the open complex systems with anomalous diffusion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2009 00:40:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2009 21:08:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-29"}
